HEADWORD: Broadsword
<hw>Broad"sword`</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A sword with a
broad blade and a cutting edge; a claymore.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I heard the <qex>broadsword's</qex> deadly clang.</q> <rj><qau>Sir
W. Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

